menuconfig SAMPLES_ANDROID
	bool "Android app samples"
	depends on ANDROID_SDK
	help
	  You can build sample Android Apps using Gradle here.

	  These samples demonstrate how to use Gradle and the Android SDK
	  from within the Linux kernel build system to build Android Apps natively.

	  If unsure, say N.

if SAMPLES_ANDROID

config SAMPLE_ANDROID_MINIMAL
	tristate "Minimal Android App"
	help
	  This option builds a minimal Android App using Gradle.

	  The build system will invoke Gradle to compile the app and
	  produce an APK file.

	  If unsure, say N.

endif # SAMPLES_ANDROID
